fields.content: I had a conversation with Mary JO. Im fine with the follow up to the specific incident & the handling of the corporate affairs contribution. However Im really concerned (&very cynical) about what might be happening; suspect lhis was not by coincidence. Inn not sure how much it was preplanned_ but Mary Jo can share with several different scenarios that we brainstormed: Mary Jo promised to keep on alert for unusual activity in the current 3 markets and 'shouz3ink is to think about awyeihes there are any preventalive steps we can/take. Page 1 Mary long
